Main Axis Alignment
 -->justify-content
Cross Axis Alignment
-->align-self
-->align-items
-->align-content
-->place-content
***allows you to align content(Box(Grp of element)) along both the block and inline directions at once
-->place-self: start end;(indivitual element)
-->place-items:--(multiple indivitual element)

